    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Issue 1 - DLT buffer flow"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Found in Project",
        "ECARX FX11",
        "RTC Ticket",
        "NA"
      ],
      "rows": []
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Analysis"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In the bootloader code, the print function \"fbl_tracestring\", use teset_data1 buffer to receive the string that will be printed. But the teset_data1 size =1, this array will overflow."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Solution"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Expand the teset_data1 size to 80 bytes."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Affected Project",
        "Fix Status",
        "Gerrit/RTC linkage"
      ],
      "rows": [
