    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Issue 3 FBL QM Log"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Found in Project",
        "ECARX FX11",
        "RTC Ticket",
        "RTC1-1767327"
      ],
      "rows": []
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Analysis"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "When copying QMErrorlog, the array testQmBuffer exceeded the bounds and the isEnteredProgSession boolean variable was changed to true, resulting in inability to enter the programming session and erase flash failure"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Solution"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "expand testQmBuffer array size to 80 bytes.",
        "add array index value check. If the index value exceed the bound value, not copy data."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Fix Status"
    },
